text: Madison Olsen (born April 7, 1995) is an American freestyle skier who competes internationally. She was raised in Park City, Utah. She participated at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:American female freestyle skiers Category:Olympic freestyle skiers of the United States Category:Freestyle skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics
